Description: # Example1
        ```python
        from coolwait import pelangi
        pelangi("Please wait...",delay=5,tab=2)
        print("hello world")
        ```
        
        # Example2
        ```python
        import coolwait
        from threading import Thread
        from coolwait import pelangi
        
        t=Thread(target=pelangi, args=("LOADING...",delay=None,tab=2))
        t.start()
        
        def do_something():
            import requests
            req=requests.get("https://google.com")
            coolwait.stop=True
            return req.text
        
        run=do_something()
        t.join()
        print(run)
        ```
        
